幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9ef06b40df6afc9066bbc3b65a8ecdd9ed310e5","tid":1538750,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c1e3d282964104e72c86792ed68773afeb0df0","tid":1538750,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"唔通有人會衝美領咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定你講緊全日？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf622b4573be581891a6cb65f0f8797fe3872ebd","tid":1538750,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"做哂又冇哂行動 post 架?推返哂上頂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccb9663eb84124faccfd20a8124a5f77db7974e","tid":1538750,"uid":49575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYFsNtt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYFsNtt.gif&h=9c453921&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e816139d309037a4f0b9b7c5b39cc1623ab60a24","tid":1538750,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"無地方需要勇武 除非有藍屍 黑警襲擊"},{"pid":"8b59f7640bd50fc0c0bbb16c6758e05bfa87adeb","tid":1538750,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"247b76b00ae0da52bf75c2b10712ec3768cc2b22","tid":1538750,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"一齊打經濟戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵制藍色餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br